(6)Information Services Group, University of Edinburgh, EH8 9YL Edinburgh, 
United Kingdom.
(7)Human Paleoecology and Archaeometry Laboratory, Department of Anthropology, 
University of Nevada, Reno, NV 89557-0096.
(8)Museum of Natural and Cultural History, University of Oregon, Eugene, OR 
97403.
(9)Department of Applied Sciences, Faculty of Health and Life Sciences, 
Northumbria University, NE1 8ST Newcastle Upon-Tyne, United Kingdom.
(10)Department of Human Anatomy and Physiology, Faculty of Health Sciences, 
