Improving wellbeing of community-dwelling people with mild cognitive impairment: 
the SENIOR (SystEm of Nudge theory based ICT applications for OldeR citizens) 
project.

Cammisuli DM(1), Pietrabissa G(2), Castelnuovo G(2).

