[Disability adjusted life years lost due to acute, chronic disability and 
premature death in arterial hypertension].

[Article in Spanish; Abstract available in Spanish from the publisher]

Villarreal-Ríos E(1), Montoya-Cruz G(2), Vargas-Daza ER(1), Galicia-Rodríguez 
L(1), Escorcia-Reyes V(3), Cu-Flores LA(4).

Author information:
(1)Unidad de Investigación Epidemiológica y en Servicios de Salud Querétaro, 
